    <subfield code="a">Dynamical photon production and <math altimg="si1.gif" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><msubsup><mrow><mi mathvariant="italic">v</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>γ</mi></mrow></msubsup></math> in the quark-gluon plasma</subfield>
